    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the garlic is softening, add the <strong>soy sauce </strong>and <strong>toasted sesame oil</strong> to the can with the <strong>reserved pineapple juice</strong> – this is your<strong> pineapple stir-fry sauce</strong></p>",
