    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the garlic has softened, add the <strong>cornflour</strong> to the pan and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Add the <strong>king prawns</strong> and <strong>pineapple stir-fry</strong> <strong>sauce</strong> to the pan and cook for 4-5 min or until the prawns are cooked through and the sauce is nice and sticky</p>",
